accessibility.text: "I want to learn about my roots."
You do more research on the program. The next day at school...
Many friends confront you and ask in a judgmental tone, "Why aren't you going to study abroad at a "cool" country, like AUS or UK or some other Western country?"
"There's a lack of appreciation of unfamiliar cultures."
